items.name: Sony-Vegas-Full
items.description: Sony Vegas, now known as Vegas Pro, is a professional video editing software that offers a wide range of features for video and audio editing.

items.name: Sapphire-Plugin
items.description: The Sapphire Plugin, developed by Boris FX, is a high-end suite of visual effects plugins widely used in video editing and post-production software like Adobe Premiere Pro, After Effects, Avid Media Composer, and VEGAS Pro. Sapphire is known for its high-quality effects, performance optimization, and extensive customization options.

items.name: fishards
items.description: An action-packed multiplayer game, made in Godot, where you can battle friends as a fish wizard.
